name: Marsian Cosmos Vault
description: Behold the pinnacle of Thunder Vault's hierarchy - the Diamond Rank, an interstellar marvel named the Marsian Cosmos Vault. Crafted from otherworldly materials designed for space travel, this vault symbolizes a cosmic odyssey. Its environment showcases celestial crystals amidst space battleships and robots, underscoring a journey beyond Earth. The backdrop illustrates the Martian landscape with distant views of Saturn, evoking a sense of otherworldly beauty and the boundless expanse of the cosmos.
